{"tid":1960933,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「立法會前哨」今日屋企收到呢張嘢","createTime":"2020-04-06T12:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T14:05:41.000Z","uid":114360,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd3f55390da6471f99b62809d12d13ec819543b1","tid":1960933,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MrrFNJF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMrrFNJF.png&h=d6794b84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iytABCo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiytABCo.png&h=73d89c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對家靜靜雞已經陸續開始做嘢，派埋d抗疫物資收買人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔夠一個月就截止登記啦，身邊仲有人未登記就記得叫佢哋登記，唔好做deadline fighter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />附上後生仔選民登記比例遠低於中老年圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2rrZiS0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2rrZiS0.jpg&h=742e66b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d5e18270fa2681c576b850e9fe89cc00914f979","tid":1960933,"uid":114360,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"【做左選民登記未？點樣登記？】<br />\n➡️檢查是否已登記做選民<br />\n（包括 立法會地方選區 及 功能界別）<br />\n👉🏻<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/welcome.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2Fwelcome.jsp&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=48eccb3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/welcome.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n➡️地方選區選民新登記申請表<br />\n👉🏻<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=1081b18c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n（新登記地方選區選民將自動成為功能界別：區議會（第二）選民）<br />\n<br />\n➡️功能界別選民新登記申請表<br />\n（適用於申請成為區議會（第二）/專業界別 選民）<br />\n👉🏻<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=7117f69d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\n➡️遞交方式<br />\n👉🏻郵寄（九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓）<br />\n👉🏻傳真（2891 1180）<br />\n👉🏻電郵方式（form@reo.gov.hk）<br />\n👉🏻上傳至政府網上平台（<a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/upload_form_reo1.jsp）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk%2Feto%2Fch%2Fupload_form_reo1.jsp%EF%BC%89&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=0249e4cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/upload_form_reo1.jsp）</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 每名選民可享有最多兩張個人票（地方選區、功能組別）及一張公司票（團體選民）<br />\n<br />\n#立法會 #選舉 #選民登記"},{"pid":"d3346b9c6ed15e0ea76773377ea4b3f490312b09","tid":1960933,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:34:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"be35b0b95660b2c28c11156bffc25bcc3a9f4b82","tid":1960933,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:34:37.000Z","msg":"唔好以為贏到區會就真係贏<br />\n仲有立會依個大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d17c0d450083404830f71919376ae63864f3958","tid":1960933,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"登記做選民"},{"pid":"2cfebd319f3867fa70e59dcae1beefa478bb8b44","tid":1960933,"uid":30520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re